<br>
We figured we could have an event Where everyone can <br>
meet up to play.  Like Saturday. We can all gather in the east coomons or in the dessert(Nro or Sro). and have a tournament to see who is the strongest. We will have diferent branches for our levels.(I.E. lvls 6 through 8 and a lvl 9 through 11 and so on).<br>
<br>
<br>
 We can all donate 10 to 20 platinum into a pool and who ever wins the tourniment out of that branch wins the prize money.  Heck if you want to we can even donate a magical weapon/item.  Ill donate my Sentry Maul for one of the prizes.<br>
<br>
I am not to good at oranizing these events so I am hoping to get some help organizing this thing(providing everyone wants to do it).<br>
If you are interested please let me know.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your time Fellas  =)<br>
<br>
Inouva<br>
<br>
<br>
